    "transcript": "User: This call may be recorded for quality and training purposes. Thanks for calling Pivot Point Orthopaedics. Would you like to create a demo patient profile? If so, I just need your first and last name.\nAI: Hi. Actually, I'm calling to book an appointment for, uh, next Monday, Wait. No. Actually, can we do can we do Wednesday instead? And also, is there parking at your office?\nUser: I can help with the appointment and the parking question. Let me check the scheduling options first. We have openings around that time. Do you prefer morning or afternoon on Wednesday?\nAI: Afternoon would be better for me.\nUser: Let me check the afternoon options for Wednesday.\nAI: Great. While you're checking that, can you also tell me about the parking situation?\nUser: Let me check the afternoon slot first, then I can help with the parking question.\nAI: Okay. Sounds good.\nUser: Let me check the afternoon options for Wednesday.\nAI: Sure. Thanks.\nUser: Connecting you to a representative. Please wait.\nAI: Actually, oh, actually, I was hoping you could\nUser: You've reached the Pretty Good AI test line.\nUser: Goodbye.\nAI: goodbye.\n",
